    "body": "Can't you just put the drop functionality in chromium as you would in the\nchrome browser?  There is standard html for that.  Someone correct me if\nI'm wrong.\n\nOn Mon, Feb 2, 2015 at 9:51 PM, Marcus Ferrario notifications@github.com\nwrote:\n\n> Would it ever be considered to implement the Cocoa drag-drop API into\n> atom-shell? This way file such as .zip could be dragged to desktop or even\n> dragged while still downloading etc.\n> \n> https://developer.apple.com/library/mac/documentation/Cocoa/Conceptual/DragandDrop/Tasks/DraggingFiles.html\n> \n> â€”\n> Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub\n> https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/issues/1085.\n"
